text: Frasinu River may refer to: * Frasinu, a tributary of the Bistrița in Gorj County * Frasinu, a tributary of the Cracăul Alb in Neamț County * Valea Frasinului, a tributary of the Dâmbovița in Argeș County * Frasinu, a tributary of the Lotrioara in Sibiu County == See also == * Frasinu (disambiguation) * Frasin River (disambiguation) * Frăsinet River (disambiguation)
title: Frasinu River
